Race.SpecificTitle: Parishwide Proposition -- 4 Mills Continuation - PJ - 10 Yrs.
Race.FullText: Shall the Parish of Allen, State of Louisiana (the "Parish"), be authorized to continue to levy a special tax of four (4) mills on all the property subject to taxation in the Parish (an estimated $516,200 reasonably expected at this time to be collected from the levy of the tax for an entire year), for a period of ten (10) years beginning with the year 2023 and ending with the year 2032, for the purpose of improving, maintaining and supporting the Courthouse and Jail of the Parish?

Race.SpecificTitle: Village of Reeves Prop. No. 1 of 5 -- Wet/Dry-6%PkgAlcoh. - M&BOA
Race.SummaryText: Village of Reeves Proposition No. 1 of 5
Race.FullText: Shall the sale of beverages of alcoholic content containing not more than six percent alcohol by volume be permitted by package only and not for consumption on the premises in the village of Reeves, Allen Parish, Louisiana?

Race.SpecificTitle: Village of Reeves Prop. No. 2 of 5 -- Wet/Dry-6%ConAlcoh. - M&BOA
Race.SummaryText: Village of Reeves Proposition No. 2 of 5
Race.FullText: Shall the sale of beverages of alcoholic content containing not more than six percent alcohol by volume for consumption on the premises be permitted in the village of Reeves, Allen Parish, Louisiana?

Race.SpecificTitle: Village of Reeves Prop. No. 3 of 5 -- Wet/Dry-1/2%ConAlcoh. - M&BOA
Race.SummaryText: Village of Reeves Proposition No. 3 of 5
Race.FullText: Shall the sale of beverage alcohol containing one-half of one percent alcohol by volume and above for consumption on the premises be permitted in the village of Reeves, Allen Parish, Louisiana?

Race.SpecificTitle: Village of Reeves Prop. No. 4 of 5 -- Wet/Dry-1/2%PkgAlcoh. - M&BOA
Race.SummaryText: Village of Reeves Proposition No. 4 of 5
Race.FullText: Shall the sale of beverages of alcoholic content containing one-half of one percent alcohol by volume and above by the package only and not for consumption on the premises be permitted in the village of Reeves, Allen Parish, Louisiana?

Race.SpecificTitle: Village of Reeves Prop. No. 5 of 5 -- Wet/Dry-Restaurant - M&BOA
Race.SummaryText: Village of Reeves Proposition No. 5 of 5
Race.FullText: Shall the sale of beverages of high and low alcoholic content be permitted only on the premises of restaurant establishments which have been issued an "R" permit as defined by law in the village of Reeves, Allen Parish, Louisiana?
